interfaces.name: Option

components.name: ButtonComponent
components.templateData:
<p-button
  [loading]="loading"
  type="button"
  label="{{ label }}"
  class="p-button-{{ type }} {{ size }} {{ type }}-{{ style }}"
  icon="pi {{ !loading ? icon : '' }}"
  iconPos="{{ !loading ? iconPos : '' }}"
  [pTooltip]="tooltip"
  [tooltipPosition]="tooltipPosition"
  [badge]="badge"
>
</p-button>

InputTextComponent
components.templateData:
<mat-form-field *ngIf="formGroup" [formGroup]="formGroup" appearance="outline">
  <input
    pInputText
    matInput
    [formControlName]="controlName"
    pTooltip="Enter your username"
  />
</mat-form-field>
